        "prerequisite": "*Mortal Herald Dedication*",
        "critical_success": "Any creature that attempts to target the anathema creature with a beneficial effect must succeed at a DC 5 flat check or the action is disrupted. This curse remains until removed by *cleanse affliction* or a similar effect, or an atone ritual. In addition, the creature gains weakness 10 to spirit damage for 1 minute.",
